'''Club Atlético Boca Unidos''' (mostly known simply as '''Boca Unidos''') is an [[Argentina|Argentine]] [[association football|football]] and [[basketball]] club from [[Corrientes Province]]. The football squad currently plays in the [[Primera B Nacional]], the second division of [[Argentine football league system]].
At the end of the 2006–07 season Boca Unidos promoted from [[Torneo Argentino B]] to the [[Torneo Argentino A]] via play-off. On 21 June 2009, the squad won another promotion which allowed it to play in the [[Primera B Nacional]], where has remained since.<ref>[http://www.afa.org.ar/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=9626%3Aboca-unidos-es-campeon-y-ascendio-a-la-primera-b-nacional&Itemid=78 "Boca Unidos es campeón y ascendió a la Primera B Nacional"] at [[Argentine Football Association|AFA]] website, 21 June 2009</ref>
