{{Infobox Basketball club | name = DVO/Accountor | logo = | imagesize = | leagues = [[Korfbal League]] | founded = {{Start date and years ago|1946| df=yes}} | history = | arena = [[DVO/Accountor-hal]] | capacity = | location = [[Bennekom]], [[Netherlands]] | colors = | president = [[Iwan van den Berg]] | coach = [[Ben Crum]] | championships = | website = [http://dvo-korfbal.nl] }}
'''CKV DVO/Accountor''' (christelijke korfbal vereninging Door Vriendschap Omhoog) is a [[Dutch people|Dutch]] [[korfball|korfball club]] located in [[Bennekom]], [[Netherlands]]. The club was founded in 1946<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dvo-korfbal.nl/home/vereniging/over-dvo/|title=Over DVO/Accountor....|last=|first=|date=|website=dvo-korfbal.nl|publisher=|access-date=2 April 2016}}</ref> and they play their home games in the [[DVO/Accountor-hal]]. The team plays in green shirts and white shorts / skirts.
==History==
DVO/Accountor joined the [[Korfbal League]] in the 2010/11 season and has been represented in the top division since then.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.telegraaf.nl/telesport/20433268/__PKC_dwarsboomt_KZ_richting_Ahoy__.html|title=PKC dwarsboomt KZ richting Ahoy|last=|first=|date=10 April 2010|website=telegraaf.nl|publisher=|access-date=2 April 2016}}</ref> In 2015 Chinese Taipei international Alice Huang joined the team from Bennekom, but that was not a success. She ended in the second team.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ikf.org/taiwanese-women-join-dalto-dvo-in-netherlands-league/|title=Taiwanese women join Dalto, DVO/Accountor in Netherlands' league|last=|first=|date=18 October 2015|website=ikf.org|publisher=|access-date=2 April 2016}}</ref>
